HEADWORD: Meconic
<hw>Me*con"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ belonging
to the poppy, fr. <?/ the poppy: cf. F.
<ets>m⟦eacute⟧conique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to, or obtained
